text.data-name: Authorize MainStay.xyz with your Google Drive, DropBox or OneDrive.
Upload the files to the newly created /MainStay folder in your cloud service.
Select the files in MainStay.xyz to attest them and obtain a proof.
Share the attested files with 3rd parties. Any recipient can use the MainStay.xyz service with their cloud to verify them.

tspan.tspan: with their cloud to verify them.
